There are 3 different nationalities: british, colombian, dutch
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rugby, sailing
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, scooter, train
 1. the scientist is the fan of house##1
 2. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is the fan of house##1
 4. the mechanic is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 6. the mechanic is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 7. the fan of house is the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the dutch is the person watching comedy movies##1
 9. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
10. the fan of house is the person drinking iced-tea##1
11. the person driving the scooter is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |      3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | water      | coffee      |
| Music-Genre          | house | punk      | pop      |
| Job           | scientist  | paramedic  | mechanic    |
