 2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the scientist##3
 3. the person traveling to prague is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
 4. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the frog##1
 5. the chinese is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the scientist##1
 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
 9. the security-guard is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |       3       |
