 6. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an odd position##4
 8. the photographer is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 9. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
10. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating peach##1
11. the person driving the van is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
